NOTE ON THE EMBEDDED BOOK TEXT

The MIT license above covers the SOFTWARE only — the MCP server code, scripts,
and configuration. It does NOT cover the book text embedded in
`src/book-data.ts`, which is:

  "Democracy Without Politicians: Government By the People"
  by Terrill "Terry" Bouricius (Routledge, 2026),
  (c) the author, licensed CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 (Open Access).

That text is included here verbatim with the author's express permission,
granted 2026-06-23, on the condition that this tool surface his actual words
rather than AI-generated summaries. The text may be redistributed only under
CC BY-NC-ND 4.0: non-commercial use, with attribution, and no derivatives of
the text. A free Open Access copy is at
https://www.taylorfrancis.com/books/9781041125549
